{"tha-ap283:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap283:0.2":"Pannadayakavagga ","tha-ap283:0.3":"Pannadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap283:1.1":"“Pannasale nisinnomhi, ","tha-ap283:1.2":"pannabhojanabhojano; ","tha-ap283:1.3":"Upavitthanca mam santam, ","tha-ap283:1.4":"upagacchi mahaisi. ","tha-ap283:2.1":"Siddhattho lokapajjoto, ","tha-ap283:2.2":"sabbalokatikicchako; ","tha-ap283:2.3":"Tassa pannam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap283:2.4":"nisinnam pannasanthare. ","tha-ap283:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap283:3.2":"yam pannamadadim tada; ","tha-ap283:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap283:3.4":"pannadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap283:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap283:4.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap283:4.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap283:4.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap283:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pannadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap283:6.1":"Pannadayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}